Definition: of very poor quality or condition
Example: deplorable housing conditions in the inner city; woeful treatment of the accused; woeful errors of judgment
Synonyms: execrable, miserable, noun, state, miserableness, woeful, wretched, attribute, wretchedness, of, very, poor, quality, or, condition, housing, conditions, in, the, inner, city, treatment, accused, errors, judgment
Category: adj.all
